{"aggs":[],"params":{"fontSize":11,"markdown":"## Welcome to SOF-ELK®

This platform consists of a pre-configured, fully functional Elastic Stack configuration. It ingests various log formats and includes several dashboards to present the data in useful formats. While the platform and project were created for various SANS Courses, SOF-ELK is maintained as community resource.

This dashboard displays a summary of data that has been loaded. If you do not see summary information below, you either haven't loaded any data yet or you may need to adjust the time frame in scope with the time range selector above.

When you're ready, [select a dashboard from the list](/app/dashboards#/list) to start exploring data.","openLinksInNewTab":false},"title":"SOF-ELK® VM Intro","type":"markdown"}
